<h3>Price Is Not the Only Cost</h3>
<p>A $49/month tool that saves 3 hours per week has a different ROI than a $299/month tool that saves 4 hours. Factor in setup time, learning curve, and maintenance overhead. The cheapest tool often costs the most when you count the hours spent configuring it.</p>
